1: Add a playlist save function

playlist load NAME: replaces the current playlist with the loaded one                   > accessible for everyone
playlist save:      saves the currently loaded playlist                                 > accessible for owner
playlist save NAME: if playlist loaded: renames it, if not, saves the current playlist  > accessible for everyone
playlist unload:    sets the playlist to be the one that you fill by using -p           > accessible for everyone
playlist del NAME:  deletes the playlist with the given NAME                            > accessible for admin, owner
playlist list:      lists all playlists                                                 > accessible for everyone


